      <title>Galderma 股东计划在 IPO 后减持 12 亿美元股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/galderma-sponsors-look-to-shed-1-2-billion-stake-after-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士护肤品巨头高德美集团 (Galderma Group AG) 刚刚上市几个月，就获得了欧洲今年最大的首次公开募股之一的成绩，其私募股权支持者正寻求出售价值 12 亿美元的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/galderma-sponsors-look-to-shed-1-2-billion-stake-after-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 16:06:06 GMT</pubDate>
